title: The Walking Dead - Vol. 16 - A Larger World
description:
The Walking Dead - Vol. 16 - A Larger World.cbr - English

Hi everyone.

This is the actual Volume 16, not the six issues bunched together. Not that there's anything wrong with that.

It seems to be the only Volume missing in all the torrents I've looked through.

I finally found it and thought I'd share. 

So update your files. It sure made me feel good, but then I'm a little OCD
